{"tid":791812,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想知其實反trump嘅人係咪都係反智?","createTime":"2018-08-24T05:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T06:00:20.000Z","uid":182864,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c300a57261b65ab72d2b6b5dbc555fb940773d0c","tid":791812,"uid":182864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:54:08.000Z","msg":"真心想知<br />\n我覺得trump做嘅嘢都係為自己國家好<br />\nBuild the wall 將班非法移民送翻去自己嘅第三世界<br />\n同贏國玩貿易戰 促成南北韓邦交<br />\n同俄佬同架仔玩得好埋<br />\n就業率自70年代以嚟最低<br />\n第一個由一開始就俾班同性戀合法結婚嘅總統<br />\nLGBTQ 平權 佢身為一個基督徒都有支持<br />\n退TPP 引返班國企翻嚟美國開廠<br />\n南非逼害白人都話會搵人研究吓咩事<br />\n近年嚟有邊個總統做到佢咁好?<br />\n奧巴馬年代就同美國係水魚 周圍派糖搞到美國蝕到仆街<br />\n呢家trump話要 America First 又有邊個政棍夠薑做?<br />\n<br />\n講翻當時選trump個時嘅demographics<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/134722_e96d5d17c208dfc1af67ba2762bffdaa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F134722_e96d5d17c208dfc1af67ba2762bffdaa.png&h=c4e4392c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希拉利淨係識得拉攏班左膠<br />\n唔記得原來pro-trump個班玩memes已經稱霸成個 /pol/   <br />\nflint/ chicago又俾班民主黨玩殘晒<br />\n唔投trump投邊個?<br />\n<br />\n之後班左膠想impeach佢做乜鳩<br />\n其實佢地知唔知總統落台就會由副總統頂上<br />\n而mike pence仲撚痴線<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/133140_08f33a8685d643551a11323fb6c5c211.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F133140_08f33a8685d643551a11323fb6c5c211.png&h=4348e4af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反LGBT反到出晒名 一上台隨時推翻晒以前啲平權政策<br />\n咁究竟左膠想快啲收皮定點<br />\n淨係識得玩white guilt<br />\n定係其實成班都係真心膠 戇鳩鳩咁?<br />\n<br />\nGod Emperor Trump 稱霸全球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4240591bbfe9c8dcbf784b7450bb78721749ab1b","tid":791812,"uid":178690,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:00:20.000Z","msg":"有名你叫左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班剩係為political correct而行動<br />\n你睇希拉利參選拉票果時人地問佢點解要投佢<br />\n佢第一句就答因為佢會成為第一任女總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}